---
// About.astro
---
<section class="section bg-surface-alt" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-layout">
      <!-- Left: Mission -->
      <div class="about-mission">
        <div class="section-label">✦ Our Mission</div>
        <h2>AI should be accountable.<br/>Not a black box that gets banks fined.</h2>
        <p>
          The financial system is undergoing a once-in-a-generation transformation. 
          Agentic AI has the power to save billions in operational costs and eliminate human error in critical workflows. 
          But that promise collapses the moment a regulator asks "why did the AI do that?" and no one can answer.
        </p>
        <p>
          We built Phronesis because we believe the gap is not a technical one — it's an infrastructure one. 
          The tools to safely deploy AI at enterprise scale already exist. 
          What was missing was the <strong>accountability layer</strong> that makes those deployments legally defensible.
        </p>
        <p>
          Just like the aviation industry didn't abandon flight when crashes happened — 
          they built better recorders — the financial industry doesn't have to choose between AI innovation and regulatory compliance. 
          Phronesis is that recorder.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Founder / Company -->
      <div class="about-right">
        <!-- The team card -->
        <div class="about-card card">
          <div class="about-avatar">M</div>
          <div class="about-info">
            <div class="about-name">Madan</div>
            <div class="about-title">Founder · QuirkyLabs.ai</div>
            <div class="about-location mono">📍 Bengaluru, India</div>
          </div>
          <a href="mailto:madan@quirkylabs.ai" class="btn btn-ghost about-contact-btn">
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/></svg>
            madan@quirkylabs.ai
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Technical credibility -->
        <div class="tech-cred card">
          <div class="tech-cred-label mono">// Technical Architecture</div>
          <div class="tech-stack">
            <div class="tech-item">
              <span class="tech-icon">⚙</span>
              <div>
                <div class="tech-name">High-Velocity Backend</div>
                <div class="tech-desc">Event-stream architecture, purpose-built for ledger semantics</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
              <span class="tech-icon">📡</span>
              <div>
                <div class="tech-name">OpenTelemetry Native</div>
                <div class="tech-desc">Ingests CNCF standard traces — no custom SDK, zero agent changes</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
              <span class="tech-icon">🔒</span>
              <div>
                <div class="tech-name">Cryptographic Integrity</div>
                <div class="tech-desc">Hash-chained append-only ledger — tamper-evident by design</div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="tech-item">
              <span class="tech-icon">🌐</span>
              <div>
                <div class="tech-name">DORA/SR 26-2 Alignment</div>
                <div class="tech-desc">Structured output maps directly to regulatory reporting requirements</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Status -->
        <div class="company-status card">
          <div class="status-items">
            <div class="status-item">
              <span class="status-key mono">Stage</span>
              <span class="badge badge-amber">Private Beta</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
              <span class="status-key mono">SOC-2</span>
              <span class="badge badge-cyan">In Progress</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
              <span class="status-key mono">Looking for</span>
              <span class="badge badge-green">Design Partners</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-item">
              <span class="status-key mono">GitHub</span>
              <a href="https://github.com/madan-quirkylabs" class="badge badge-blue" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">madan-quirkylabs</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.about-layout {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.85fr;
  gap: 4rem;
  align-items: start;
}

.about-mission .section-label { margin-bottom: 1.25rem; }
.about-mission h2 { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
.about-mission p { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
.about-mission p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
.about-mission strong { color: var(--color-cyan); font-weight: 600; }

.about-right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }

/* Avatar card */
.about-card {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}
.about-avatar {
  width: 52px;
  height: 52px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-cyan), var(--color-blue));
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.4rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--color-bg);
  flex-shrink: 0;
}
.about-info { flex: 1; }
.about-name { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); }
.about-title { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); }
.about-location { font-size: 0.72rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); margin-top: 0.15rem; }
.about-contact-btn { font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; white-space: nowrap; }

/* Tech stack */
.tech-cred {}
.tech-cred-label { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
.tech-stack { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
.tech-item { display: flex; gap: 0.75rem; align-items: flex-start; }
.tech-icon { font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem; }
.tech-name { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-text); margin-bottom: 0.15rem; }
.tech-desc { font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.45; }

/* Status */
.company-status {}
.status-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem; }
.status-item { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 0.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem; }
.status-key { font-size: 0.68rem; color: var(--color-text-dim); }

@media (max-width: 900px) {
  .about-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
}
</style>
